title: Ebro In The Morning - The Day After Summer Jam 2022 + The March For Our Lives
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/13/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing last night's Summer Jam concert and all of the surprises that took place! Ebro big up's Erica Ford and the crew clowns Burna Boy!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
